targets.rawSql:
SELECT
  latest.timestamp,
  m.key        AS name,
  (m.value->>'cset')::float AS cset,
  (m.value->>'cmon')::float AS cmon,
  m.value->>'pol'           AS pol
FROM (
  SELECT * FROM magnet
  ORDER BY timestamp DESC
  LIMIT 1
) AS latest,
LATERAL jsonb_each(latest.magnet_data) AS m(key, value)
ORDER BY
  CASE m.key
    WHEN 'AK11D1'   THEN 1
    WHEN 'AK18D1'   THEN 2
    WHEN 'AH18'     THEN 3
    WHEN 'BSM1'     THEN 4
    WHEN 'K18Q1'    THEN 5
    WHEN 'K18Q2'    THEN 6
    WHEN 'K18D2'    THEN 7
    WHEN 'K18Q3'    THEN 8
    WHEN 'K18O1'    THEN 9
    WHEN 'K18Q4'    THEN 10
    WHEN 'K18S1'    THEN 11
    WHEN 'K18CM1'   THEN 12
    WHEN 'K18CM2'   THEN 13
    WHEN 'K18S2'    THEN 14
    WHEN 'K18Q5'    THEN 15
    WHEN 'K18Q6'    THEN 16
    WHEN 'K18D3'    THEN 17
    WHEN 'K18BRS3'  THEN 18
    WHEN 'K18BRQ7'  THEN 19
    WHEN 'K18BRD4'  THEN 20
    WHEN 'K18BRQ8'  THEN 21
    WHEN 'K18BRD5'  THEN 22
    WHEN 'DORA'     THEN 23
    ELSE 999
  END;
